            <title>[PDFBOX-4395] Accent positioning in Type1 fonts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4395</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When viewed in PDFBox Debugger, the accents in the attached PDFs are in wrong position. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a patch to fix this. The asb argument specifies the left side bearing of the accent glyph. It must be subtracted from the x coordinate.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
